# Account 1
IMAPAccount gmail
Host imap.gmail.com
Port 993
User sycamoremoon376@gmail.com
PassCmd "pass sycamoremoon376@gmail.com"
AuthMechs LOGIN
TLSType IMAPS

IMAPStore gmail-remote
Account gmail

MaildirStore gmail-local
Path ~/Mail/gmail/
Inbox ~/Mail/gmail/INBOX
Subfolders Verbatim

Channel sycamoremoon376@gmail.com
Expunge Both
Far :gmail-remote:
Near :gmail-local:
Patterns "[Gmail]/*" INBOX
CopyArrivalDate yes
Sync All
Create Both
SyncState *
MaxMessages 0
ExpireUnread no

